      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of August 20 article on plans to redevelop former Long Island Developmental Center in Huntington, which misstated center's function (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article last Sunday about plans to redevelop the former Long Island Developmental Center in Huntington misstated its function. It was a residence for the mentally retarded and developmentally disabled of all ages; the Sagamore Children's Center, adjacent to the Developmental Center and still in operation, is a children's psychiatric hospital.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
